data.description: Home sweet home! Subject property features 4 ample bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms. As you make your way towards the kitchen you will find beautiful quartz countertops, white cabinetry, and recess lighting. There is laminate wood flooring through out, and a very spacious backyard. The covered patio is perfect for entertainment. Best part of all, this home will have paid-off solar panels! No need to worry about those hot summer days. This gorgeous home is conveniently located minutes away from Marie Kerr Park, The Palmdale Amphitheater, Rancho Vista Golf Course, and the Antelope Valley Mall.
